         <abstract id="aspace_8602f044fc440e41a86e3bf74be4ab63">The collection consists of pencil and charcoal drawings depicting scenes of Yale and New Haven, Connecticut drawn by Loveday Yates in the 1940s and 1950s.</abstract>
